Create a new feature flag called "$FLAG_NAME" with type "$FLAG_TYPE" (boolean, string, number, json).

Use the Flagify CLI with `-y` to skip confirmation:
```
flagify flags create $FLAG_NAME -y --type $FLAG_TYPE --description "$DESCRIPTION"
```

Flag name rules: kebab-case only (e.g. `new-checkout-flow`). No camelCase, snake_case, or spaces.
